Package au.gov.naa.digipres.xena.kernel.normalise

Class Summary
AbstractDeNormaliser AbstractDeNormaliser is an empty implementation of TransformerHandler that is able to be overridden to De-Normalise Xena files.
AbstractNormaliser Normalisers may find it convenient to use this abstract class.
BinaryToXenaBinaryNormaliser Normalise a binary file to a Xena binary-object file.
ExportResult The Export result object represents the result of a Xena export.
NormaliserDataStore Deprecated. An object that just stores a collection of relevant object related to the normalisation process.
NormaliserManager This class is responsible for managing all things pertaining to normalisers.
NormaliserResults created 31/03/2006
XenaBinaryToBinaryDeNormaliser Denormaliser for converting a Xena binary-object file to a plain binary object.
